Simple Harvesting Script by BeanzoUK
--------------------------------------------------

Overview
--------------------------------------------------
A lightweight standalone script that automates
basic harvesting actions.

This script was created to simplify repetitive
harvesting tasks by automatically performing the
required actions in sequence.

--------------------------------------------------
Features
--------------------------------------------------
- Automates harvesting actions
- Simple, lightweight and configurable.
- Easy to run.
- Minimal setup required.

--------------------------------------------------
Installation
--------------------------------------------------
1. Download this repository as a ZIP
2. Extract the ZIP file
3. Place the script in your desired folder

--------------------------------------------------
Notes
--------------------------------------------------
- Use responsibly
- Make sure the script is configured correctly
  before running

